text: E4 is a television channel that broadcasts in the United Kingdom. The "E" stands for entertainment, It started on 18 January 2001. On 14 December 2009 E4 started a High Definition version of their channel on Sky+ HD. Channel 4 owns E4. ==Programmes they have shown== *Rude Tube *Made in Chelsea *Tattoo Fixers *New Girl *Brooklyn Nine Nine *The Inbetweeners *PhoneShop *School of Comedy *Tool Academy *Coach Trip *The 100 *Rich Kids of Instagram Category:2001 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:British television channels Category:Channel 4
